/*******************************************************************************
 * KeyOption ( modifierKeys )
 *
 * @parameter modifierKeys: The modifierKey output to test for from the
 * Get ( ActiveModifierKeys ) or Get ( TriggerModifierKeys ) functions.
 *
 * @return True (1) if the option key is indicated by the modifierKeys value, False (0) otherwise
 *
 * @history 2011-04-21 - Jeremy Bante <http://scr.im/fugue> - Created
 * @history 2012-04-02 - Jeremy Bante <http://scr.im/fugue> - Accepting the
 * modifierKeys parameter.
 ******************************************************************************/

Mod ( Div ( modifierKeys ; 8 ) ; 2 )